Package: ggmagnify
Title: Create a Magnified Inset of Part of a "ggplot" Object
Version: 0.2.0
Author: David Hugh-Jones
Maintainer: David Hugh-Jones <davidhughjones@gmail.com>
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "Hugh-Jones", , "davidhughjones@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Creates a magnified inset of a ggplot, with projection lines and
  borders around the target area and inset, plus optional shadow. Rectangular,
  elliptical or arbitrary regions can be magnified. Works with facets and maps. 
  Geoms can optionally be recomputed within the inset area.
